  "prompt": "Which is the best institute in India for doing a hands on course in ethical hacking?",
  "response": "There are several reputable institutes in India that offer hands-on courses in ethical hacking. Some of the top ones include:\n\n1. **Indian School of Ethical Hacking (ISOEH)**: Based in Kolkata, ISOEH offers a variety of courses in ethical hacking and information security, providing practical, hands-on training.\n\n2. **Institute of Information Security (IIS)**: With locations in Mumbai and Pune, IIS is known for its industry-relevant training programs in ethical hacking and cybersecurity.\n\n3. **National Institute of Electronics & Information Technology (NIELIT)**: With various centers across India, NIELIT offers certification courses in information security and ethical hacking.\n\n4. **Simplilearn**: An online platform that provides a comprehensive ethical hacking course with practical labs and projects, allowing you to learn at your own pace.\n\n5. **Hackers School**: Located in Hyderabad, Hackers School offers specialized training in ethical hacking with a focus on real-world applications.\n\n6. **Appin Technology Lab**: Offers training in cybersecurity and ethical hacking across multiple locations in India, providing hands-on lab sessions.\n\nWhen choosing an institute, consider factors like the course curriculum, hands-on training opportunities, faculty expertise, industry recognition, and placement support. Additionally, reviews and testimonials from past students can provide valuable insights into the quality of education and training provided.",
